:{"banned":"0","descriptors":"Gewalt","rating":"16","rating_generated":"1","required_age":"16","use_age_gate":"0"}},"recommendations":{"total":13320},"release_date":{"coming_soon":false,"date":"19 Apr, 2013"},"required_age":0,"reviews":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/233720/extras/edge_magazine_logo.png?t=1726238747\" />  \u201cFew games take that odd, occasional gulf between what you intend to happen and what actually occurs on screen and fill it with such comedy.\u201d Edge<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/233720/extras/guardian_logo_trans.png?t=1726238747\" />  \u201cNo matter how sophisticated you like your humour, seeing someone fail under the influence of a goofy physics engine is always funny.\u201d The Guardian<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/233720/extras/red-bull-logo.png?t=1726238747\" />  \u201cFamously (and intentionally) difficult to control and often hilarious, this game requires a strong stomach and no morals whatsoever.\u201d Red Bull<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/233720/extras/Gamespot_logo_trans.png?t=1726238747\" />  \u201cSurgeon Simulator 2013 is hardly a simulation, but it makes medical malpractice an absolute delight.\u201d Gamespot 80%<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/233720/extras/GTlogo_trans.png?t=1726238747\" />  \u201cA dark, gruesome, and hilarious take on this life-saving vocation.\u201d GameTrailer 80%","screenshots":[{"id":0,"path_full":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/233720/ss_2649ec090dbd500cc561a1dce6d844a6068ce242.1920x1080.jpg?t=1726238747","path_thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/233720/ss_2649ec090dbd500cc561a